Jessica Revell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jessica_Revell 0 Jessica Revell (born 13 December 1994) is an English actress and singer, best known for her TV role as Mandy "Elektra" Perkins in Tracy Beaker Returns and in the BBC spin-off series The Dumping Ground.
